{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"619","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"164企業虧錢 董事酬金反增","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2020-01-31 23:53 </span><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:&#10;12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報 記者蔡靜紋／台北報導</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>臺灣證券交易所、櫃買中心昨（<span lang='EN-US'>31</span>）日同步公布<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年上市櫃公司第二階段董監事酬金支領情形，多達<span lang='EN-US'>218</span>家公司經營虧損仍發出董事酬金，當中<span lang='EN-US'>164</span>家公司董事酬金金額甚至不減反增，其中大同虧損逾百億元，卻發<span lang='EN-US'>2,000</span>餘萬元董事酬金，平均每位董事領到<span lang='EN-US'>287.3</span>萬元，是發最多董事酬金的虧損公司。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>2018</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>年財報虧損仍發出董事酬金金額前十高的上市櫃公司中，除大同高達<span lang='EN-US'>2,321</span>萬元外，華豐、茂迪、逸達等三家都發出逾千萬元董事酬金；雷虎、麗嬰房、立德、聯合再生等四家也各有<span lang='EN-US'>900</span>餘萬元；無敵、駿熠電各發出<span lang='EN-US'>850</span>萬元、<span lang='EN-US'>762</span>萬元。其中僅麗嬰房、聯合再生董事酬金低於前一年，其他八家都比前一年增加。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>如依每位董事平均領取酬金金額比較，大同每席領<span lang='EN-US'>287.3</span>萬元，居虧損公司首位，茂迪、無敵、雷虎、麗嬰房、聯合再生、立德等六家公司董事也各領超過百萬元，華豐、一詮、皇昌亦於前十名之列，每位董事各領<span lang='EN-US'>90</span>萬元以上。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>上市櫃公司董事可能同時在公司擔任職務，領有員工薪資。如將董事酬金加計兼任員工酬金，則虧損上市櫃公司中，以威剛董事們領到<span lang='EN-US'>6,885</span>萬元最多，其次是台聯電的<span lang='EN-US'>5,473</span>萬元，第三名是<span lang='EN-US'>3,721</span>萬元的大同，<span lang='EN-US'>PCHOME</span>網家以<span lang='EN-US'>3,583</span>萬元追隨其後，聯合再生也有<span lang='EN-US'>2,640</span>萬元之譜，如興、廣運、國光生、懷特、敦泰等五家落在<span lang='EN-US'>2,000</span>萬元至<span lang='EN-US'>2,500</span>萬元之譜。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>大同董事酬金引人注目，對此，大同表示，加計兼任員工酬金總額較<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年度略高，是因<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年度酬金包括兼任員工領取<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年度獎金，公司<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年度由虧轉盈，酬金變動尚屬合理。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>相對於有些上市櫃公司虧損仍發董事酬金，有更多上市櫃公司是風光賺錢發董事酬勞。以上市公司來看，董事酬金總額前六名依序為國巨<span lang='EN-US'>10.28</span>億元、中信金<span lang='EN-US'>3.8</span>億元、台積電<span lang='EN-US'>3.78</span>億元、統一<span lang='EN-US'>3.20</span>億元、和泰車<span lang='EN-US'>2.62</span>億元、上銀<span lang='EN-US'>2.61</span>億元。</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E8%96%AA%E9%85%AC.jpg' style='width: 399px; height: 425px;' />&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟日報／提供</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源：<span lang='EN-US'>https://money.udn.com/money/story/5612/4314912</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-03","clk_count":"215"}},"__N_SSG":true}